  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/AppStoreConnectAPI\/app-event-localizations\ncrawled: 2025-12-05T18:01:00Z\n---\n\n# App Event Localizations\n\n**API Collection**\n\nCreate and update in-app event metadata that’s localized.\n\n## Endpoints\n\n- **GET \/v1\/appEventLocalizations\/{id}**\n- **GET \/v1\/appEventLocalizations\/{id}\/appEventVideoClips**\n- **GET \/v1\/appEventLocalizations\/{id}\/relationships\/appEventVideoClips**\n- **GET \/v1\/appEventLocalizations\/{id}\/appEventScreenshots**\n- **GET \/v1\/appEventLocalizations\/{id}\/relationships\/appEventScreenshots**\n- **PATCH \/v1\/appEventLocalizations\/{id}**\n- **POST \/v1\/appEventLocalizations**\n- **Delete an App Event Localization**: Delete localized metadata that you configured for an in-app event.\n\n## Objects\n\n- **AppEventLocalization**\n- **AppEventLocalizationCreateRequest**\n- **AppEventLocalizationResponse**\n- **AppEventLocalizationUpdateRequest**\n- **AppEventLocalizationsResponse**\n- **AppEventLocalizationAppEventScreenshotsLinkagesResponse**\n- **AppEventLocalizationAppEventVideoClipsLinkagesResponse**\n- **AppEventLocalizationsLinkagesResponse**\n\n## Managing App Event Metadata\n\n- **App Event Video Clips**: Create and update video clips your product page uses for the card or detail view of an in-app event.\n- **App Event Screenshots**: Create and update screenshots your product page uses for the card or detail view of an in-app event.\n\n",
